Privacy Policy & Terms of Service
Effective as of April 6, 2023
This Privacy Policy explains what personal data we collect about you and how we use your personal data, as well as the choices you have about your personal data.
This Privacy Policy applies to all our services (such as Guitar 3D Apps, Flexy Drums, Guitar Scorist, My Metronome, Music Scorist), Websites like Polygonium.com, Guitar3d.app and related services and properties we control and which we collectively here call the “Services”.
These terms of service (the “Terms”) apply to you and Polygonium Inc., a Canadian entity specified below in section “Contact us” (hereinafter, “Polygonium Inc.” or “us/we/our”) regarding your use of Polygonium Inc.’s applications, services, products, websites, and all content and software related to our services (collectively, the “Services”). Use of the Services is also governed by Polygonium’s Privacy Policy (the “Privacy Policy”) and other relevant policies.
These Privacy Policy & Terms of Service which are incorporated herein by reference, form a legally binding agreement (the “Agreement”) between you and Polygonium Inc. in relation to your use of the Services, so please read them carefully. The current valid version of the Agreement is available on the Polygonium website.
