Polygonium Inc. may update the Privacy Policy & Terms of Service occassionally by posting a new version of the Privacy Policy & Terms of Service on Polygonium.com. If there are amendments that are deemed as material changes, Polygonium Inc. will notify the users by posting a notice in the Services or by other appropriate means. Please note that your use of the Services as a user after the effective date is subject to the new Privacy Policy & Terms of Service.
