Why do we process your personal data?
We handle your personal data for the purposes outlined below, based on the following legal grounds:
To Operate and Enhance the Services
To fulfill our contract with you, it’s essential to process your information to:
Establish and manage your account within our Services (where applicable), enabling your use of our Services,
Operate and deliver the Services,
Fulfill your requests for products and services,
Communicate with you about service-related matters (e.g., confirmations, administrative notices, technical updates).
To Improve User Experience
With the goal of providing excellent services and optimizing user experience, we have a legitimate interest in processing necessary data to:
Analyze, refine, and personalize our Services and user experience,
Maintain our customer relationship with you,
Offer user support and address your inquiries and feedback,
Examine your interactions with our Services to tailor your experience,
Inform you about updates, alerts, and other Service-related news,
Identify and fix any service errors or issues,
Generate non-identifiable data from users (e.g., aggregated statistics).
To Engage Our Target Audience
In our legitimate interest to market our Services effectively and reach audiences likely to be interested, we process needed data to:
Present you with our promotions for our Services, and via email,
Inform you about our events and Service-related news,
Monitor our app installations and their sources.
To Maintain Fairness and Safety
To ensure the Services are used responsibly and to protect our operations, we legitimately process required data to:
Monitor for and prevent misuse or illegal activities, enforcing our terms or defending our legal rights,
Conduct audits of our operations.
For Analysis and Segmentation
We analyze and segment all collected data for the purposes mentioned above.
With Your Permission
Should we need to process your personal data for any purpose not covered by other legal bases under applicable law, we will seek your consent.
We may also process your data as needed to fulfill legal obligations (including responding to legal authorities and meeting tax requirements), or for other purposes compatible with the above.
We don’t make automated decisions using your personal data that significantly impact you.
Regarding Advertisements
To offer free access to content within our Services, we may display ads. For this purpose, we integrate SDKs from third-party ad partners into our Services. Depending on your privacy preferences, these ads may be contextual or personalized.
Unless you opt out of personalized advertising, our ad partners’ SDKs might collect various data to serve you relevant ads. If you opt out of personalized advertising, non-personal, contextual information, and your advertising ID may be collected for limited purposes. Our ad partners may use this information to tailor ads to your interests, among other purposes outlined above.
